ace Series in total\n\nOver 190 races to complete\nOver  30 cars to collect\nMultiplayer \nFreeroam\n\nDriven is a physics-based \"simcade\" racing game incorporating realistic car-handling and aerodynamics.\n\nVirtual steering and automatic or manual transmission.\n\n2 AI difficulty levels - extra credits awarded for racing against Pro AI.\n\nUpdated graphics for Quest 3\n\nNew Damage feature\n\n\nTake to the track and have fun!", "short_description": "Immersive first person racing on the Meta Quest 2 & 3\n\nCompete against AI to gain credits to purchase cars and gain access to races. Win the race to be added to Global Leaderboards\n\nTake part in Time Trial mode navigating obstacles - get on the Leaderboard\n\nVirtual steering and automatic/manual transmission.\n2 AI difficulty levels - extra credits awarded for racing against Pro AI\n\nUpdated graphics for Quest 3\nDamage feature"}]}, "developer_name": "MK1", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mk1vrracing.wixsite.com/driven", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "MK1", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://mk1vrracing.wixsite.com/driven", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_FEW", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "673385183287495"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["RACING", "ACTION", "ARCADE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "7837947766259924"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://sconten